# Machi! Kubeadm Full Step-by-Step Guide 🔥

## 📋 Overview - Enna Panrom?

```
🖥️  MASTER NODE (1 EC2)  →  Control Plane
🖥️  WORKER NODE (1 EC2)  →  Apps run agum
📊  MONITORING           →  Master node la install panrom
```

