## 🔧 PHASE 2: Both Nodes la Run Pannu (MASTER + WORKER same commands)

> ⚠️ **Machi Important:** Phase 2 commands RENDU nodes laye run pannu!

### Step 3: SSH Connect Pannu

```bash
# Master node ku
ssh -i "your-key.pem" ubuntu@<MASTER-PUBLIC-IP>

# Worker node ku (new terminal open pannu)
ssh -i "your-key.pem" ubuntu@<WORKER-PUBLIC-IP>
```

### Step 4: System Update

```bash
sudo apt-get update -y
sudo apt-get upgrade -y
```

### Step 5: Swap Off Pannu (Mandatory!)

```bash
# K8s ku swap vendave vendaam
sudo swapoff -a

# Permanent ah off pannu
sudo sed -i '/ swap / s/^\(.*\)$/#\1/g' /etc/fstab

# Verify
free -h
# Swap: 0 0 0  → ipdhi varudha confirm pannu
```

### Step 6: Kernel Modules Load Pannu

```bash
cat <<EOF | sudo tee /etc/modules-load.d/k8s.conf
overlay
br_netfilter
EOF

sudo modprobe overlay
sudo modprobe br_netfilter
```

### Step 7: Network Settings

```bash
cat <<EOF | sudo tee /etc/sysctl.d/k8s.conf
net.bridge.bridge-nf-call-iptables  = 1
net.bridge.bridge-nf-call-ip6tables = 1
net.ipv4.ip_forward                 = 1
EOF

# Apply pannu
sudo sysctl --system
```

### Step 8: Containerd Install (Container Runtime)

```bash
# Install
sudo apt-get install -y containerd

# Config folder create pannu
sudo mkdir -p /etc/containerd

# Default config generate pannu
sudo containerd config default | sudo tee /etc/containerd/config.toml

# SystemdCgroup enable pannu (important!)
sudo sed -i 's/SystemdCgroup \= false/SystemdCgroup \= true/g' \
  /etc/containerd/config.toml

# Restart & Enable
sudo systemctl restart containerd
sudo systemctl enable containerd

# Verify
sudo systemctl status containerd
# ✅ Active: active (running)
```

### Step 9: Kubeadm, Kubelet, Kubectl Install

```bash
sudo apt-get install -y apt-transport-https ca-certificates curl gpg

# GPG Key add pannu
curl -fsSL https://pkgs.k8s.io/core:/stable:/v1.29/deb/Release.key | \
  sudo gpg --dearmor -o /etc/apt/keyrings/kubernetes-apt-keyring.gpg

# Repo add pannu
echo 'deb [signed-by=/etc/apt/keyrings/kubernetes-apt-keyring.gpg] \
  https://pkgs.k8s.io/core:/stable:/v1.29/deb/ /' | \
  sudo tee /etc/apt/sources.list.d/kubernetes.list

# Install
sudo apt-get update -y
sudo apt-get install -y kubelet kubeadm kubectl

# Version lock (auto-upgrade agama irukkum)
sudo apt-mark hold kubelet kubeadm kubectl

# Enable kubelet
sudo systemctl enable kubelet

# Verify
kubeadm version
kubectl version --client
```

