## 👷 PHASE 4: WORKER NODE ONLY

> ⚠️ **Machi:** Indha phase commands WORKER node la MATTUM run pannu!

### Step 13: Worker Node Join Pannu

```bash
# Step 10 la copy pannina join command inga paste pannu
sudo kubeadm join 172.31.10.5:6443 --token xxxxx \
    --discovery-token-ca-cert-hash sha256:xxxxx

# ✅ Output:
# This node has joined the cluster!
```

