## 📊 PHASE 5: Monitoring Install - MASTER NODE la!

> 💡 **Machi:** Prometheus + Grafana → **MASTER NODE la install panrom**
> Worker nodes la automatically metrics collect agum (node-exporter daemonset)

### Step 15: Helm Install (Master la)

```bash
curl https://raw.githubusercontent.com/helm/helm/main/scripts/get-helm-3 | bash

# Verify
helm version
```

### Step 16: Monitoring Namespace Create

```bash
kubectl create namespace monitoring
```

### Step 17: Prometheus + Grafana Install

```bash
# Repo add pannu
helm repo add prometheus-community \
  https://prometheus-community.github.io/helm-charts
helm repo update

# Install (kube-prometheus-stack = Prometheus + Grafana + AlertManager)
helm install prometheus prometheus-community/kube-prometheus-stack \
  --namespace monitoring \
  --set grafana.adminPassword='Machi@123' \
  --set prometheus.prometheusSpec.retention=7d

# 2-3 minutes wait pannu...
```

### Step 18: Monitoring Pods Check

```bash
kubectl get pods -n monitoring

# OUTPUT (ippidhi varunum):
# NAME                                                  READY   STATUS
# prometheus-grafana-xxxxxxxxx                          3/3     Running ✅
# prometheus-kube-state-metrics-xxxxxxxxx               1/1     Running ✅
# prometheus-node-exporter-xxxxx (MASTER la)            1/1     Running ✅
# prometheus-node-exporter-yyyyy (WORKER la)            1/1     Running ✅ ← Auto!
# alertmanager-prometheus-kube-prometheus-alertmgr-0    2/2     Running ✅
# prometheus-prometheus-kube-prometheus-prometheus-0    2/2     Running ✅
```

